column5: We had another great week at milesbay camp. Thanks Matt and Jenn for a great week. We caught several walleyes for the week over 20" with the biggest at 27" we caught more peach over 10" while we was walleye fishing with one over 13" I had a over 50" musky on for 30+minutes on a hot n tot and 8lb florocarbon line. Had him by the boat 6 times so we got a good measurement on him but didnt have a net big enough for him finally the snap ring broke on the crank bait. Small mouth fishing was a little slow but caught a few. All and all a great fun week.
